import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const ProductList = (products) => {
    return (
        <>
            <tr>
                <th>
                    {product.code}
                </th>
                <th>
                    {product.name}
                </th>
                <th>
                    {product.description}
                </th>
                <th>
                    <Link exact to={'/updateproduct/' + product.code} key={product.code}> Update
                    </Link>
                </th>
                <th></th>

            </tr>
        </>
    )
}

export default ProductList
